data.description: Welcome to your new haven in the heart of Crosby, Texas! This delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home at 502 Alaska Cedar offers a perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience. As you arrive, you'll be greeted by the classic brick exterior and well-maintained façade which provide an inviting first impression. Step inside to discover a spacious and open living room bathed in natural light. This area is perfect for relaxing, entertaining guests, or simply spending quality time with your family. Nice backyard with no back neighbors.  Situated in the vibrant community of Crosby, you'll have easy access to local schools, shopping, dining, and parks. Don't miss your chance to own this wonderful home in a desirable location. Schedule a viewing today and experience all that it has to offer. Your new beginning awaits!
